    sentence = f"{subject}, " + ", ".join(clauses) + "." if len(clauses) > 0 else subject + "."

        sentence = sentence.replace("is of", "is")
        sentence = sentence.replace("was created by", "created by")
        sentence = sentence.replace("whose full name", "with a full name")
        sentence = sentence.replace("with a key person being", "with a key person")
        sentence = sentence.replace("with", "and")
```
